Christine Estabrook https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christine_Estabrook 0 Christine Estabrook is an American actress, known for her roles on the television series The Crew, Nikki, Desperate Housewives and American Horror Story; she had a recurring role on the drama Mad Men during that show's fifth season, and continuing into the sixth and seventh. She has received Obie Award and Drama Desk Award.
